                <span class="post-footers">Posted by <a rel="author" href="https://profile.typepad.com/6p014e8bbc0f91970d">NELB Staff</a> on 08/22/2020 at 04:35 PM</span> <span class="separator">|</span> <a class="permalink" href="https://kolber.typepad.com/ethics_law_blog/2020/08/anthony-j-casey-university-of-chicago-law-school-and-anthony-niblett-university-of-toronto-faculty-of-law-have-publish.html">Permalink</a>
